  "prompt": "A dashboard mockup for a neurodivergent, operator-grade, AI-powered productivity and profit platform. The dashboard is chaotic yet organized, with vibrant colors, modular panels, and playful elements. Features include a multi-persona agent selector (with icons like meme mode, hyperfocus, chaos), a one-click launchpad for new workflows, apps, merch, and memes, live profit/revenue metrics, a mutation timeline of branching projects, dopamine-trigger notifications (“10 sales! Take a bow!”), sensory mode toggles (minimal/maximal), an idea graveyard for archived concepts, an agent swarm panel showing real-time bot activity, and rapid context-switching tabs. Add ND-friendly fonts, energetic layouts, and humor (like quirky tooltips and stickers). No generic or corporate vibes—make it look unique and empowering.",
